node_modules
**/node_modules
coverage
data
tmp
*.log
# Exclude build artifacts so `railway up` never uploads a stale dist that makes
# the Docker tsc-incremental build skip recompiling (this masked mcp-server
# source changes — the native MCP tools shipped stale). The Docker builder
# rebuilds every package's dist from source, so excluding these is safe.
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo
